No. 107,

Misc.

Crummer Company et al. v. DuPont et al., Trustees, et al.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari to the Circuit Court of Appeals for *852the Fifth Circuit denied.

Robert J. Pleus, Chris Dixie and Joseph P. Lea, Jr. for petitioners. Richard W. Ervin, Attorney General of Florida, Ralph McLane, Assistant Attorney General, Henry P. Adair, Donald Russell, Charles R. Scott and H. M. Voorhis for respondents. Mr. Justice Clark took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
